answers.answer: My blood pressure has been good. I read it can be a uti also.
When i had protein was my blood pressure...

I had a trace of protein in my urine and the Dr wasn't worried at all she said as long as its just a trace, its not a big, sometimes that happens from skin particles around ur vagina. They are only worried if they find a specific amount but she said a trace isn't anything to be worried about.they found a trace of protein when I was 36 weeks I'm 38 weeks now and just went to the Dr today and baby is healthy with no issues.

title: protein in urine
